sequenceDiagram
    title Ingest routing — capability-aware dispatch (I6), both branches
    autonumber

    participant W as Watcher
    participant O as Orchestrator
    participant R as ConfigResolver
    participant PG as Postgres
    participant P as InferenceProvider (ABC)
    participant CLI as CliAgentProvider
    participant MCP as MCP server
    participant FS as Wiki FS

    W->>O: ingest_file(path)
    Note over O: mtime-then-hash gate (I1) — real content change confirmed
    O->>R: resolve(vault_id, operation="ingest")
    R->>PG: SELECT provider_config (operation > vault > global)
    PG-->>R: resolved config (provider_type, model_id, max_iter, token_budget)
    R-->>O: ProviderConfig
    O->>P: construct provider from config (I6 — key from env, never DB)
    O->>P: capabilities()
    P-->>O: ProviderCapabilities{supports_agentic_loop, mode, ...}

    alt supports_agentic_loop == True  (CLI — DELEGATED)
        O->>CLI: delegate_ingest(source_text, vault_context, token_budget=100000)
        Note over CLI: provider runs its OWN agent loop; orchestrated loop body NOT executed (AC-K2-3)
        CLI->>MCP: search_wiki / get_page (read context)
        MCP-->>CLI: PageRefs / page
        CLI->>MCP: write_page(title, content, frontmatter)
        MCP->>FS: write wiki/<type>/<slug>.md (validated, I5)
        MCP->>PG: persist_metadata + links (K5) + upsert vector
        MCP-->>CLI: PageRef
        CLI-->>O: result{pages_written, tokens, cost=$0.00}
    else supports_agentic_loop == False  (Local/API — ORCHESTRATED)
        Note over O: run orchestrated loop — see ingest-loop.mmd (max_iter + token_budget, I7)
        O->>P: analyze() then generate()/validate() loop
        P-->>O: list[WikiPage] (converged) or converged=False
        O->>FS: write each WikiPage to wiki/ (I1 upsert, I5 frontmatter)
        O->>PG: persist_metadata + links (K5) + upsert vector
    end

    O->>FS: update index.md (K3) and overview.md (F3) — both branches
    O->>PG: INSERT ingest_runs{provider_name, route, max_iter_used, total_tokens, total_cost_usd, converged} (I7)
    Note over O: if total_cost_usd > $1.00 → log WARNING, set cost_anomaly=True (inline, ADR-0009)
    O-->>W: IngestResult
